Test Data Generation: Discussion on creation of regression test datasets for AUT Test Data Augmentation: Strategies for enhancing and expanding existing test data to improve AUT robustness and testing coverage. Performing Coverage Gaps on Test Data: Methods for identifying and addressing gaps in the current test data to ensure comprehensive AUT evaluation. Evaluation: Review of the primary evaluation metrics and processes used to assess the quality, safety, and performance of AUT Gathering Insights: Discussion on mechanisms for collecting, analyzing, and translating evaluation results into actionable feedback for AUT improvement and risk mitigation. Extension to other frameworks :- Extension to complementary evaluation frameworks, such as RAGAS and DeepEval. Post discussion align on the proposed Gen AI Assurance approach across all key areas and gather constructive feedback.
